


=Groups=

This application lets you keep track of all application groups.

[grupos-listado.png]

==List of groups==

In the list of groups you will find the most important pillars of registration:

- **Ref .:**  Numeric code that identifies the group.
- **Name:**  Group name.
- **Description:**  Group Description.


===Listing Options===

On each record. You can perform a series of actions that are represented by the following icons:

- [../../lib/silk/icons/magnifier.png][../../lib/silk/icons/pencil.png][../../lib/silk/icons/delete.png]: Check / Edit / Delete Record.


