==Groups form==

This is the application of groups, it may add, modify and view all data of the groups classified in different tabs: main data, application permissions, data on the registry modifications and assignments to folders.

===Data Tab Group===

In this tab you can view and modify the main details of the group. Here we relate all information fields.

[grupos-formulario.png]

- **User (*):**  Group name.
- **Description:**  Descrpcion group.


(*) **Required when creating or modifying a group fields.**

===Application permissions tab===

In this tab you can apply the permissions to the group.

